Subject: [PATCH 1/2] fix: improve responsiveness and broken features
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

- Fix Gemini model name (gemini-3-flash-preview → gemini-2.0-flash)
- Fix Gemini API key fallback (was incorrectly using Firebase API key)
- Make loginTime optional in User type (was required but never set)
- Fix all oversized headings across pages (text-7xl/8xl → responsive sm/md breakpoints)
- Fix mobile bottom padding on all pages (pb-36 to clear BottomNav)
- Rewrite AIAssistant: full multi-turn chat, quick prompts, clear button, send on Enter
- Fix BottomNav: add missing Calendar & Resources links (now 8 items with active labels)
- Fix Calendar: clickable days show event detail panel, colored border per category
- Fix Resources: replace stale-closure snapshot merge with ref-based approach
- Fix StudyTools advisor chat: proper multi-turn context, markdown rendering, fixed alignment
- Fix Profile theme toggle: initialize from DOM class instead of hardcoded 'dark'
- Reduce mobile padding on all pages for better small-screen layout
